  <p>I started learning Webdevelopment and programming in april 2021, 9 months ago.</p>
  <p>I had to become better with Ruby and his framework : Rails.</p>
  <p>This also was a good opportunity pratice both JavaScript and SCSS.</p>
  </div>
</div>

