  <h4>Technologies used</h4>
  <p>I wanted to make a project in less than 3 weeks (its far from perfect).</p>
  <p>The only library I used is Devise (for authentication), there is not any other library.</p>
  <p>51% HTML - 29.5% Ruby - 11.8% SCSS - 7.7% JavaScript</p>
